label\"><foreignObject height=\"20\" width=\"32.8819465637207\"><div style=\"display: inline- block; white- space: nowrap;\"xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><span class=\"edgeLabel\">push</span></div></foreignObject></gtransform=\"translate(478.86371994018555, 115.5)\" class=\"edgeLabel\"><g transform=\"translate(- 24.06684112548828, - 10)\"class=\"label\"><foreignObject height=\"20\" width=\"48.13368225097656\"><div style=\"display: inline- block; white- space: nowrap;\"xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><span class=\"edgeLabel\">trigger</span></div></foreignObject></gtransform=\"translate(478.86371994018555, 155.5)\" class=\"edgeLabel\"><g transform=\"translate(- 16.44097328186035, - 10)\"class=\"label\"><foreignObject height=\"20\" width=\"32.8819465637207\"><div style=\"display: inline- block; white- space: nowrap;\"xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><span class=\"edgeLabel\">push</span></div></foreignObject></g>><g class=\"edgeLabel\"><gtransform=\"translate(0, 0)\" class=\"label\"><foreignObject height=\"0\" width=\"0\"><div style=\"display: inline- block; white- space: nowrap;\"xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><span class=\"edgeLabel\"></span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g><g class=\"nodes\"><gtransform=\"translate(636.1857719421387, 249.25)\" id=\"flowchart- ECR- 4224\" class=\"node default 默认\">>rect height=\"35\"width=\"216.5104217529297\" y=\"- 17.5\" x=\"- 108.25521087646484\" ry=\"0\" rx=\"0\" style=\"\" class=\"basic label- container\"></rect><gtransform=\"translate(- 100.75521087646484, - 10)\" style=\"\" class=\"label\">foreignObject height=\"20\" width=\"201.5104217529297\"><divstyle=\"display: inline- block; white- space: nowrap;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><span class=\"nodeLabel\">Elastic ContainerRepository</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform=\"translate(636.1857719421387, 89.25)\" id=\"flowchart- CodeDeploy- 4228\"class=\"node default默认\"><rect height=\"35\" width=\"99.453132629453\" y=\"- 17.5\" x=\"- 49.726566314697266\" ry=\"0\" rx=\"0\" style=\"class=\"basic label- container\"></rect><g transform=\"translate(- 42.226566314697266, - 10)\" style=\"\" class=\"label\"><foreignObjectheight=\"20\" width=\"84.45313262939453\"><div style=\"display: inline- block; white- space: nowrap;\"xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><span class=\"nodeLabel\">CodeDeploy</span></div></foreignObject></gtransform=\"translate(386.39844131469727, 135.5)\" id=\"flowchart- CodeBuild- 4227\" class=\"node default 默认\">>rect height=\"35\"width=\"86.796875\" y=\"- 17.5\" x=\"- 43.3984375\" ry=\"0\" rx=\"0\" style=\"\" class=\"basic label- container\"</rect><gtransform=\"translate(- 35.8984375, - 10)\" style=\"\" class=\"label\"><foreignObject height=\"20\" width=\"71.796875\"><div style=\"display:inline- block; white- space: nowrap;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><spanclass=\"nodeLabel\">CodeBuild</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform=\"translate(51.6328125, 74.25)\"id=\"flowchart- developer- 4225\" class=\"node default\">rect height=\"35\" width=\"87.265625\" y=\"- 17.5\" x=\"- 43.6328125\" ry=\"0\" rx=\"0\" style=\"\"class=\"basic label- container\"></rect><g transform=\"translate(- 36.1328125, - 10)\" style=\"\" class=\"label\"><foreignObject height=\"20\"width=\"72.265625\"><div style=\"display: inline- block; white- space: nowrap;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><spanclass=\"nodeLabel\">开发人员</span></div></foreignObject></g></g><g transform=\"translate(210.57378768920898, 74.25)\"id=\"flowchart- GitHub- 4226\" class=\"node default 默认\"><rect height=\"35\" width=\"64.85243225097656\" y=\"- 17.5\" x=\"- 32.42621612548828\"ry=\"0\" rx=\"0\" style=\"\" class=\"basic label- container\"></rect><g transform=\"translate(- 24.92621612548828, - 10) \" style=\"\"class=\"label\"><foreignObject height=\"20\" width=\"49.85243225097656\"><div style=\"display: inline- block; white- space: nowrap;\"xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><span class=\"nodeLabel\">GitHub</span></div></foreignObject></g></g></svg>。\n\n\n有了OAuth认证，开发者不再需要手动管理到AWS的令牌，在CodeBuild之后的授权管理是完全无令牌的，因为可以使用AWS框架。\n\n## GitHub和AWS CodePipeline集成\n\n使用OAuth认证。\n\n你可以从 \"CodePipeline > Connections > Create a connection \"中创建一个连接。\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/173198376-c5593755-f6a8-45d3-a084-0b0aa54b9727.png)\n\n## Elastic Container Registory，准备CodeBuild。\n\n首先初始化ECR并创建CodeBuild，因为CodePipeline配置需要它。\n\n### 弹性容器注册表\n\n从 \"Amazon ECR > Create Repository \"创建一个资源库。在这种情况下，假定有一个私人图像。\n\n\n我们使用了GitHub的OAuth认证，链接到CodePipeline，并使用CodeBuild自动推送到ECR来展示如何做到这一点。\n\n## GitHub和AWS CodePipeline集成\n\n使用OAuth认证。\n\n你可以从 \"CodePipeline > Connections > Create a connection \"中创建一个连接。\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/173198376-c5593755-f6a8-45d3-a084-0b0aa54b9727.png)\n\n## Elastic Container Registory，准备CodeBuild。\n\n首先初始化ECR并创建CodeBuild，因为CodePipeline配置需要它。\n\n### 弹性容器注册表\n\n从 \"Amazon ECR > Create Repository \"创建一个资源库。在这种情况下，假定有一个私人图像。\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/173199828-f633c796-47b1-4c37-82ea-bb1d7ae18540.png)\n\n### CodeBuild配置。\n\n`CodeBuild > 创建项目`。\n\n这一次，授予权限，以便构建Docker镜像。你也应该使用buildpec文件。\n其他设置，如图像和日志管理，可以按照你的意愿进行配置。\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/173199385-9857e08e-2158-4292-8ee2-b501d8a5a7b5.png)\n## 配置IAM设置。\n\n\n##创建一个CodePipeline\n\n`CodePipeline > Create pipeline`。\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/173198769-407d678d-3523-4232-9170-a142b456f062.png)\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/173198785-a516c306-894c-4251-acb5-df134830d5a6.png)\n\n根据你刚刚创建的连接，选择你想使用的版本库和你想发布的分支。\n\n### CodeBuild配置。\n\n`CodeBuild > 创建项目`。\n\n这一次，授予权限，以便构建Docker镜像。你也应该使用buildpec文件。\n其他设置，如图像和日志管理，可以按照你的意愿进行配置。\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/173199385-9857e08e-2158-4292-8ee2-b501d8a5a7b5.png)\n\n## 配置IAM设置。\n\n`IAM > Roles > codebuild- *****`。\n\n在CodeBuild中创建/使用的角色需要被授予ECR的权利。\n\n在这次检查中，AmazonEC2ContainerRegistryFullAccess是通过 \"添加权限>附加策略 \"授予的。\n\n##创建一个CodePipeline\n\n`CodePipeline > Create pipeline`。\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/173198769-407d678d-3523-4232-9170-a142b456f062.png)\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29157528/173198785-a516c306-894c-4251-acb5-df134830d5a6.png)\n\n根据你刚刚创建的连接、CodeBuild和ECR，选择你要使用的存储库和你想发布的分支。\n\n至于部署步骤，这次被跳过了。\n\n## buildspec.yml\n\n以下列形式创建一个buildpec.yml，并在版本库下创建它。\n\n```yml\nversion: 0.2\nphases:\n  pre_build:\n    commands:\n      - aws ecr get-login-password --region ap-northeast-1 | docker login --username AWS --password-stdin *****.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com\n  build:\n    commands:\n      - docker build -t container-image . \n  post_build:\n    commands:\n      - docker tag container-image *****.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/container-image:latest\n      - docker tag container-image *****.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/container-image:$CODEBUILD_RESOLVED_SOURCE_VERSION\n      - docker push -a *****.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/container-image\n```\n\n可用的环境变量，如`$CODEBUILD_RESOLVED_SOURCE_VERSION`，可以在下面几页找到。\n\n[构建环境中的环境变量](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ja_jp/codebuild/latest/userguide/build- env- ref- env- vars.html)\n\n上述设置会导致自动推送到ECR。下一次，将推送的ECR镜像部署到ECS上。\n",
